{"tid":343982,"cid":20,"subCid":0,"title":"北區有冇戥肽鋪介紹？","createTime":"2017-08-02T02:23:42.000Z","updateTime":"2017-08-03T16:56:20.000Z","uid":10660,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"f952cec189030f5424dfd7af186552a327d00856","tid":343982,"uid":10660,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-02T02:23:42.000Z","msg":"架車行到90-100 堂軚就震到乜咁<br />\n試下戥下肽睇下有冇效果。<br />\n<br />\n仲有架車堂軚偏左少少，車房話上手撞過黎所以咁。係咪做四輪定位都冇用？"},{"pid":"cc8704dce18e04e2a9d03e0911432421af203caa","tid":343982,"uid":23897,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-02T07:53:10.000Z","msg":"lm"},{"pid":"6ebfd7e6bbe9b91c8e0808b13486b642bd606a47","tid":343982,"uid":59466,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-02T07:57:15.000Z","msg":"樓主買果時竟然無發現到問題<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c5103b79fed2980ba3b151ca2f8aef201513edff","tid":343982,"uid":10660,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-02T17:02:13.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>樓主買果時竟然無發現到問題<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n我第一次買車乜都唔識<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n啱啱驗完車諗住新一年新開始，平平地就搞下，貴就留返啲錢買下架車"},{"pid":"104070d75b3c89426b526b4a67488d382f9d96fa","tid":343982,"uid":42732,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-03T07:18:09.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>樓主買果時竟然無發現到問題<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n我第一次買車乜都唔識<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n啱啱驗完車諗住新一年新開始，平平地就搞下，貴就留返啲錢買下架車</blockquote><br />\n搵d熟車既朋友一齊睇嘛<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2448f56a208cb143c95f07f62288736e3d88e13d","tid":343982,"uid":10660,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-03T09:44:29.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>樓主買果時竟然無發現到問題<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n我第一次買車乜都唔識<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n啱啱驗完車諗住新一年新開始，平平地就搞下，貴就留返啲錢買下架車</blockquote><br />\n搵d熟車既朋友一齊睇嘛<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n當時冇呀，得一個有揸車既朋友，佢揸左輪都話ok冇乜特別。<br />\n之後行車証就到期，朋友介紹車房代驗check完先知pk。<br />\n不過架野用黎操車，純粹戥胎價錢平同減少安全問題先去整。<br />\n<br />\nbtw，其實係咪間間鋪戥胎都差唔多，冇乜鑊氣？因為都叫第一次整，怕俾人水，求其搞兩下就打發我走<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c76cb0af081fd1f37ee3f8319a976ba4c53e9682","tid":343982,"uid":1515,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-03T12:43:10.000Z","msg":"點解唔上架先買<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 如果落咗訂都唔肯比你上架就擺明身有屎啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0fbbbaab1f1c508fe5dde46bd863e81d18c55624","tid":343982,"uid":10660,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-03T16:56:20.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>點解唔上架先買<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 如果落咗訂都唔肯比你上架就擺明身有屎啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n我朋友幫我試完車，再上埋架，去埋運輸處轉完名先俾錢。<br />\n只能怪我第一次買車咩都唔識啦...同埋個價位得佢一個賣，女友又話款車好得意好想要。<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n星期六求其去間胎鋪戥下胎，希望冇伏<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}